title: Pacheco
body: This family name comes from Antão Pacheco and the commander Gomes Pacheco, individuals who came to Madeira in the mid-15th century. Pedro Pacheco, son of Gomes Pacheco, justified his nobility in 1535.

Antão Pacheco: Individual who came to Madeira in the mid-15th century
Gomes Pacheco: Commander who came to Madeira in the mid-15th century
Pedro Pacheco: Son of Gomes Pacheco, justified his nobility in 1535

XV: Arrival of Antão Pacheco and the commander Gomes Pacheco in Madeira
1535: Justification of nobility by Pedro Pacheco
